[src:persistent-segment-versioned/segment-tree] The segment tree can be generalized to higher dimension spaces, in the form of multi-level segment trees.
[src:persistent-segment-versioned/segment-tree] In higher dimensional versions, the segment tree stores a collection of axis-parallel (hyper-)rectangles, and can retrieve the rectangles that contain a given query point.
